summary: I am a qualified Russian/German teacher with over 9 years of experience with a primary focus on online teaching. During that time I've been helping students to achieve their goals (from feeling more confident in a new language environment to passing an important exam), giving both group and face-to-face lessons, developing courses and webinars, and managing a small online-business.
